            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EEli%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20disciplining%20his%20sons%20because%20he%20was%20more%20concerned%20about%20their%20opinion%20of%20him%20than%20God's%20opinion%20of%20him.%20So%20God%20asked%20him%2C%20%22Why%20do%20you%20honor%20your%20sons%20more%20than%20me-for%20you%20and%20they%20have%20become%20fat%20from%20the%20best%20offerings%20of%20my%20people!%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(1%20Samuel%202%3A29).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EChristians%20should%20value%20God's%20Word%20and%20His%20opinion%20far%20more%20than%20they%20value%20the%20opinion%20of%20man.%20Jesus%20rebuked%20the%20Jews%20because%20they%20made%20no%20effort%20to%20obtain%20the%20true%20praise%20that%20comes%20only%20from%20God.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20more%20concerned%20about%20receiving%20praise%20from%20one%20another%20(John%205%3A44).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESomeone%20once%20said%2C%20%22Never%20be%20concerned%20about%20what%20others%20think%20about%20you%2C%20because%20they%20don't%20think%20about%20you!%22%20In%20reality%2C%20most%20people%20really%20think%20primarily%20about%20themselves%2C%20and%20their%20opinions%20will%20not%20count%20when%20you%20stand%20before%20almighty%20God.%20The%20day%20will%20come%20when%20all%20men%20will%20be%20silent%2C%20and%20you%20alone%20will%20give%20an%20account%20for%20your%20choices%20and%20convictions.%20Where%20will%20your%20fans%20or%20critics%20be%20then%3F%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20you%20place%20God's%20opinion%20above%20all%20else%2C%20it%20may%20cost%20you%20a%20friend.%20However%2C%20at%20the%20final%20judgment%2C%20all%20eternity%20will%20record%20your%20integrity%20before%20Him.%20Stand%20firm%20in%20the%20truth%2C%20and%20honor%20God%20above%20anyone%20else%2C%20even%20family.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
