            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Samuel%202%3A22-4%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_22%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20Eli%20was%20very%20old%2C%20but%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20what%20his%20sons%20were%20doing%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20He%20knew%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20his%20sons%20were%20seducing%20the%20young%20women%20who%20assisted%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ETent%20of%20Meeting.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Some%20manuscripts%20lack%20this%20entire%20sentence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_23%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EEli%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20been%20hearing%20reports%20from%20all%20the%20people%20about%20the%20wicked%20things%20you%20are%20doing.%20Why%20do%20you%20keep%20sinning%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_24%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20must%20stop%2C%20my%20sons!%20The%20reports%20I%20hear%20among%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20people%20are%20not%20good.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_25%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20someone%20sins%20against%20another%20person%2C%20God%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A25%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20judges.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20can%20mediate%20for%20the%20guilty%20party.%20But%20if%20someone%20sins%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20who%20can%20intercede%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20Eli%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20wouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20their%20father%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20already%20planning%20to%20put%20them%20to%20death.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_26%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20boy%20Samuel%20grew%20taller%20and%20grew%20in%20favor%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_27%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Warning%20for%20Eli%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Family%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20a%20man%20of%20God%20came%20to%20Eli%20and%20gave%20him%20this%20message%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20revealed%20myself%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A27%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EDid%20I%20reveal%20myself.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20your%20ancestors%20when%20they%20were%20Pharaoh%26%23x2019%3Bs%20slaves%20in%20Egypt.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_28%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20chose%20your%20ancestor%20Aaron%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A28a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eyour%20father.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20from%20among%20all%20the%20tribes%20of%20Israel%20to%20be%20my%20priest%2C%20to%20offer%20sacrifices%20on%20my%20altar%2C%20to%20burn%20incense%2C%20and%20to%20wear%20the%20priestly%20vest%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A28b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ean%20ephod.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20as%20he%20served%20me.%20And%20I%20assigned%20the%20sacrificial%20offerings%20to%20you%20priests.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_29%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20why%20do%20you%20scorn%20my%20sacrifices%20and%20offerings%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20give%20your%20sons%20more%20honor%20than%20you%20give%20me%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20you%20and%20they%20have%20become%20fat%20from%20the%20best%20offerings%20of%20my%20people%20Israel!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_30%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20I%20promised%20that%20your%20branch%20of%20the%20tribe%20of%20Levi%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A30%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethat%20your%20house%20and%20your%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20would%20always%20be%20my%20priests.%20But%20I%20will%20honor%20those%20who%20honor%20me%2C%20and%20I%20will%20despise%20those%20who%20think%20lightly%20of%20me.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_31%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20time%20is%20coming%20when%20I%20will%20put%20an%20end%20to%20your%20family%2C%20so%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20serve%20as%20my%20priests.%20All%20the%20members%20of%20your%20family%20will%20die%20before%20their%20time.%20None%20will%20reach%20old%20age.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_32%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20watch%20with%20envy%20as%20I%20pour%20out%20prosperity%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20But%20no%20members%20of%20your%20family%20will%20ever%20live%20out%20their%20days.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_33%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20few%20not%20cut%20off%20from%20serving%20at%20my%20altar%20will%20survive%2C%20but%20only%20so%20their%20eyes%20can%20go%20blind%20and%20their%20hearts%20break%2C%20and%20their%20children%20will%20die%20a%20violent%20death.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A33%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Dead%20Sea%20Scrolls%20and%20Greek%20version%2C%20which%20read%20%3Cem%3Edie%20by%20the%20sword%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3Edie%20like%20mortals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_34%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20to%20prove%20that%20what%20I%20have%20said%20will%20come%20true%2C%20I%20will%20cause%20your%20two%20sons%2C%20Hophni%20and%20Phinehas%2C%20to%20die%20on%20the%20same%20day!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_35%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20I%20will%20raise%20up%20a%20faithful%20priest%20who%20will%20serve%20me%20and%20do%20what%20I%20desire.%20I%20will%20establish%20his%20family%2C%20and%20they%20will%20be%20priests%20to%20my%20anointed%20kings%20forever.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_2_36%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20cla